The blaze was started inside the facility last week and spread through two communal cells. JOHANNESBURG - The Department of Correctional Services is investigating afteravideo of a fire at the Krugersdorp prison was taken by an inmate. The blaze was startedinside the facility last week and spread through two communal cells. Four detaineesand six officials had to be treated for smoke inhalation. Three people have been linked to the fire. Department spokesperson Manelisi Wolela said, We are investigating this matter, inclusive of an illegal cellphone that has taken the video is now placed on social media platforms and gone viral. WATCH: Fire at Krugersdorp prison [WARNING: VIDEO CONTAINS EXPLICIT LANGUAGE]